cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the performance of two popular techniques in deep learning, Dropout and Batch Normalization, and their combination. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
